data.description: Charming 3-bedroom ranch boasting numerous updates throughout! Recently replaced water heater ensures efficiency and reliability. Enjoy a well-lit ambiance with updated recessed lighting in the kitchen, bedroom, and living room. The bathtub has been refinished, complemented by new recessed lighting above for a spa-like atmosphere. The backyard is perfect for gatherings with a cozy firepit, and the main floor is adorned with new blinds. Conveniently located near shopping and restaurants in a quiet neighborhood, this home is also in close proximity to schools, making it an ideal and comfortable living space.
